		<h3>文本格式化<span>-</span></h3>
		<div class="u-list">
			<h4>[<span>-</span>]URI</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><em>encode/decode</em><a href=""></a><span>
					<a href="http://www.cnblogs.com/shuiyi/p/5277233.html">参考资料1</a>、
